		<title>Mayo Clinic study identifies mechanism behind immunotherapy resistance in lung cancer</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-study-identifies-mechanism-behind-immunotherapy-resistance-in-lung-cancer/
		
